编译和安装请看INSTALL

项目主页：http://www.surfchen.org/wiki/Nali



wget https://github.com/asiacny/nali/blob/master/nali-0.2.tar.gz?raw=true
tar zxvf nali-0.2.tar*
cd nali-0.2/
./configure
make
sudo make install

更新ip库 https://github.com/WisdomFusion/qqwry.dat
wget https://github.com/WisdomFusion/qqwry.dat/blob/master/20180510/qqwry.dat?raw=true -O /usr/local/share/QQWry.Dat

用法：
mtr -n www.qq.com | nali
ping www.baidu.com |nali
nali-ping
